      <title>美国银行的 Hartnett 表示，债券上涨将拖累 2024 年初股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/bofa-s-hartnett-says-rising-bonds-will-drag-on-stocks-early-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行 (Bank of America Corp.) 的迈克尔·哈特尼特 (Michael Hartnett) 表示，2024 年第一季度股市将遭受重创，因为债券上涨将预示着经济增长放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/bofa-s-hartnett-says-rising-bonds-will-drag-on-stocks-early-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 09:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构与持有人会面，碧桂园地方债券测试迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/country-garden-bondholders-are-asked-to-consider-delaying-early-repayment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碧桂园控股有限公司 (Country Garden Holdings Co.) 于 10 月份首次在美元债券上违约，下周将面临考验，以避免在当地票据上遭遇同样的命运——监管机构表示试图避免这种结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/country-garden-bondholders-are-asked-to-consider-delaying-early-repayment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 06:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
